decks.notes: The main concept of this deck is to utilize the graveyard as a resource to quickly fill the board with creatures such as Narcomoeba, Ichorid, and Prized Amalgam. The deck aims to create a powerful board presence through efficient self-mill with cards like Golgari Thug and Stinkweed Imp, while also disrupting the opponent with cards like Grief and Force of Will. By utilizing cards like Bazaar of Baghdad and Hollow One, the deck can quickly overwhelm the opponent and win through a combination of attacking and combo potential.
